<h1><span id="Mengarini_Variation">Mengarini Variation</span></h1>
<p>This opening is an interesting variation of the Wing Gambit. The idea is to prepare b4 with a3. The main continuation is 2...Nc6 although many moves are possible.
</p>
<p>1.e4 c5 2.a3
